show.title: Betrayed By My Beloved Wife
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/t52GUb
show.description: A timid musician, Arjun, gets wrongfully accused of a crime and falls from love into ruin at the hands of his once-adoring wife, Tanya, now his cruel tormentor. Humiliated and broken, Arjun finds an unexpected lifeline in Rhea, a kind surgeon who believes in his forgotten talent. As Tanya’s obsession spirals and dark secrets begin to surface, Arjun must reclaim his voice—and his life—in this gripping tale of betrayal, resilience, and redemption.
